Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这个空间我们称之为"宇宙"{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in a place we call "The Universe."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小行星和彗星 地球的天上眷属{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Asteroids and comets-- Earth's celestial relatives.{\r}
