Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}问题不在于我们在将来是否会遭受打击{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The question is not whether we'll be struck in the future...{\r}
